videos.headline: Snell refuses to be denied from scoring fourth rushing TD
videos.description: Kentucky's Benjamin Snell Jr. appears to be stuffed short of the goal line, but he will not give up and pushes the entire pile by himself to get into the end zone for his fourth touchdown of the game putting the Wildcats up 55-42.
